profile:
Hi and Welcome to my listing!

My name is Jean-Marc and I have 10+ years in the general construction and renovation industry. I also have over 2 years of experience as a general contractor. I work closely with Rona/Pont Masson and Home Depot for the majority of my project materials. My specialties include completing top to bottom basements and secondary dwellings for homeowners that want to have an additional income in their home. Why the name "Income Property" and specialize in the upkeeps of apartment for property managers. I also specialize in drywall repair and asphalt shingles roof repair. 

Call me for a free quote today at 613-551-7417!
services: No job is too small! Framing, Drywall, Flooring (ceramic, vinyl, hardwood), Siding and much more!
specialities: Finishes/Details and trim work (baseboards, doors and windows, crown moulding)
warranty_terms: Yes, materials dependent (see further for details)
